Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:04.52,School,Sign 0004,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Shisuda Municipal \NElementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.99,0:00:03.97,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Gouda Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:06.36,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look like it, but I'm \Na first-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.73,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend, Sunakawa Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:12.11,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I call him "Suna."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:14.24,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,We live next to each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.41,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,and we've known each other since kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:15.55,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign 0016,0000,0000,0000,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:20.29,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we friends, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:22.66,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:24.08,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.80,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,That guy... Isn't he kinda sketchy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:32.10,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:35.93,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Get off this train at the next station!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:43.78,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:49.32,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:53.07,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Yamato Rinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:54.17,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:57.94,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:00:58.62,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.62,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:07.20,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she's fallen in love with Suna, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:15.67,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, throughout my long history with Suna, \Nthat's been a common occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:19.76,Message,Sign 0118,0000,0000,0000,,4/23 Yamato Rinko  \N\NSubject: Morning~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:19.76,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:24.58,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Today's another nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:28.60,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll have a good day, Gouda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.96,0:01:30.15,SFX-Red,Sign 0130,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(212,269)}*blush*
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.32,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And I've made a decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.68,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be their cheerleader,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:38.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,to ensure they can have a \Nsuccessful relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.29,Title1,Sign 0311,0000,0000,0000,,My Romance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.29,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,One more round!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.56,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,So, in this fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.80,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,Japan modernized, following the \NMeiji government's inception...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.30,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,The Charter Oath of Five Articles
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:30.48,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,illuminates the Meiji government's basic policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:30.48,SFX-BlueWhite,Sign 0328,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(288,1)}Stare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:34.15,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0331,0000,0000,0000,,Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:34.15,SignA,Sign 0331,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.45,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.15,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he's reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.87,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't he hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.23,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Really hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.27,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Try talking to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:40.78,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.78,SignA,Sign 0342,0000,0000,0000,,Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:42.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:44.28,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a handsome man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.28,SignB,Sign 0342,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(273,1)}Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.78,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.78,SignB,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(238,1)}Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.91,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(271,1)\fs18}Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:53.54,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.27,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,How long ago did Suna move here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:59.46,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,We were in kindergarten,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.72,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,so it must've been over ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.00,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I've seen him pretty \Nmuch every single day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:11.58,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,we've never talked about girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:15.23,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,so I have no idea what kind of girl he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:23.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.24,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.61,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of girl do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:34.37,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,In order to help Yamato's feelings bear fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.63,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I must know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:49.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, you always say that after you've come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's with your getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:52.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I just took a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't like we have an exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:02.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, you know you're supposed \Nto study every day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:12.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, I know this is sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but what kind of girl do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That sure is sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk AKB. Who do you like there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:21.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm not familiar with celebrities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:24.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What if you had to choose between \NSayla-san and Fraw Bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:25.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing anime now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:29.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then what about the Song \NLady or the Exercise Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the Exercise Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What about between Main-chan and Sui-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:34.77,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Main who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So the Exercise Lady, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:41.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's your conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.30,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is Yamato-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.14,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.54,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.54,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.54,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.54,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hard one to read, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:03.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to girls you like, \Nyou're like an open book.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:08.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You like anyone with whom you \Nhave a halfway decent chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You like girls who smile a lot \Nand get along with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:14.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The cute ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.49,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He might be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:23.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, let's get some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:24.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:46.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a butt every time, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:50.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is a guy's butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's a guy's butt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:56.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why I never saw that before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking at it for over ten years, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:05.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.15,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you today, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.15,SFX-BlackRed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(273,1)} You're asking that while looking at the butt tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.15,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:10.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're popular with the ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:15.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You never think about dating girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.16,SFX-BlackRed,Sign 0715,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,1)}You're way too close, man
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.17,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:26.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:30.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about what I'd have to do \Nif I dated anyone, it makes me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.67,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:34.85,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It should make you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:39.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you have a pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.17,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then why aren't you interested in girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:45.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then you are interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.99,SFX-BlackRed,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Seriously, you're too close
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, as much as any other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:56.87,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, a word of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:09.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you find girls tiring,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:11.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,refrain from acting in ways \Nthat make them fall for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:15.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm going out of \Nmy way to act like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, restrain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:20.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Response?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:24.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okaaay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "Okay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Put more feeling into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:37.37,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,The first basic sentence structure in English \Ngrammar consists of a subject and a verb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:42.41,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,It's a complete sentence, not requiring \Nan object or complement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.42,Board,Sign 0843,0000,0000,0000,,Sentence Structure #1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.92,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Stay awake, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:53.17,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,In such a sentence, the verb \Nneeds to be intransitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.43,Message,Sign 0855,0000,0000,0000,,4/24 Yamato Rinko  \N\NSubject: Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.43,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.94,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD78DD3&}It's Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:59.30,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H79A3BE&}I baked the sachertorte.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:02.18,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come over tomorrow, so you can have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:05.14,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her text?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.94,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.89,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,real colorful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:14.51,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}An example would be "I go."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:15.82,Message Body - Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A-n-y t-i-m-e w-o-r-k-s.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:19.07,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Next, let's discuss the sentence \N"I go to the park on foot."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.27,Message Body - Default,Yamato,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HC772C9&}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.33,Message Body - Default,Yamato,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.33,Message Body - Default,Yamato,0000,0000,0000,,Can I call you {\c&H79D070&}"Takeo-kun"??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:26.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap! The crap moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:38.34,Message Body - Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,T-h-e-n I w-i-l-l c-a-l-l y-o-u "Y-a-m-a-t-o," t-o-o.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.35,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:46.28,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato-san is a nice girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:49.21,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,and Suna's a nice guy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.96,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,They make a great couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.11,EyecatchA,T,0000,0000,0000,,Song
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.11,EyecatchB,T,0000,0000,0000,,Exercise
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I have to come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This way. Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:16.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:42.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:43.91,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.63,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:58.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So this is sacherotote!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.27,SignC,Sign 1058,0000,0000,0000,,sacherotote
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.97,SignC,Sign 1100,0000,0000,0000,,sachertorte
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:06.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had a more delicious chocolate cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you can eat so much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:10.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, stuffing yourself and working out \Nwould make you a sumo wrestler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.94,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:19.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sumo wrestler, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:20.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You honor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't meant as a compliment, but okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:24.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I should have thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.15,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:30.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get something for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:32.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.34,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Suna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.59,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Subtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.39,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You think so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:54.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We met when we were three,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,so we've known each other for over a decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:04.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But he's always been a great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:12.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When we were in kindergarten, I played \Nthe main part in a class play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:14.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It was {\i1}The Red Ogre Who Cried{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.46,SignD,Sign 1214,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}The Red Ogre Who Cried
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:17.50,Default - flashback,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,I think Takeo-kun should play the Red Ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.98,Default - flashback,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Ditto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.61,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.75,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the Red Ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.76,SignE,Sign 1224,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Ogre {\c&H917B57&}Who Cried
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.97,SignE,Sign 1227,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}The Red Ogre \N{\c&H917B57&}Who Cried
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:30.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,As the Blue Ogre, Suna was \Na child prodigy at acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,and made all the moms cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,My acting was more on the dumb side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:37.33,Default - flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,The boy playing the Red Ogre looks really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When we were in first grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally peed in my pants during cleanup
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:45.31,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1245,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:45.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,because I always used to \Nhold it till the last second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:49.11,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1246,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.74,SignC - Copy,Sign 1246,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,100)}Pfft
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna was in stitches,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:53.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but he soaked himself with a \Nbucketful of water with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,so no one else found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And the time I got so excited on a field trip
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:02.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,that I flipped over my bento box...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna was all in stitches again,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:07.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but he gave me more than half his bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:08.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,More than half!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:17.37,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Man, why is it that when I try to talk \Nabout what a great guy Suna is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:21.94,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I have to discuss all the embarrassing \Nthings in my past?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:32.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.60,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:38.13,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You decided to cheer them on, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:39.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:40.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:46.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna likes the Exercise Lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:48.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,and he's interested in girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:51.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.84,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.36,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,How do you help people in things like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just tasted something \Nthat isn't chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's the prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I put in one prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:10.70,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, a prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:14.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:18.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh... Yeah, the prize... is a chestnut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A chestnut...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I mean you just get to eat it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see, a prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:39.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Can I bake something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:45.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I should pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:54.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're always baking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Letting things like this slide doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:01.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:03.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.41,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.63,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You two make a great couple, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks for the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:15.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:18.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:24.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Can I text you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Like, when I want to ask you what kind \Nof cakes you like and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:35.45,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.52,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I get you, Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:39.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:43.03,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've got your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:47.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, give her your info, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I mean is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, till next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:24.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Take care on your way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, not so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:28.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:04.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:09.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Go... Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.93,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:20.40,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It never works because, in this kind of \Nsituation, I go to the falling beam...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.31,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:26.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be the knight in shining armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.67,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:37.80,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,At least she'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:45.24,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's all... that matters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Be more careful, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If it'd landed on anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:54.90,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,they'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.76,Default,Worker,0000,0000,0000,,Secure the cables, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:03.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:07.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,pretty strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, you're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:29.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I think I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:36.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:57.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, \Nyou're always helping me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:03.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:14.89,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You've walked into a pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.97,SignF,Sign 1921,0000,0000,0000,,Perm \N\N{\c&H52CAAF&}Haircut
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.72,SignG,Sign 1921,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,225)}Good Evening
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, you're stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, you'll die for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Pig Gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Old-Man Face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:53.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Those cakes were really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:04.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.89,Phone,Sign 2011,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato Rinko  \N\NIncoming Call
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.91,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.65,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep my crap together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:21.82,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to cheer them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:26.34,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,To help Yamato with her relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:29.66,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:32.67,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:35.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:40.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much for helping me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:42.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The cake was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:45.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please bake one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:46.68,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:50.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and, well....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:55.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, could it be without Sunakawa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'd like it to be just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:00.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:01.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about next weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:09.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,In front of the park fountain again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:09.79,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:13.73,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really asked Yamato \Nabout her feelings yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:20.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing Suna so many times, \NI'm sure they're solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.23,Phone,Sign 2119,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato Rinko  \N\NCall Ended  \N02m 30s
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:29.24,Default - italics,Sign 2119,0000,0000,0000,,She's finally ready to ask for \Nadvice with her relationship.
